init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There is an artsy, bespectacled version of you sitting in the back row, who's drawing something on a sketchpad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There is a dark, mysterious version of you with goth makeup and stylish clothing sitting next to a pale, frail looking version of you who is wearing

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "So we get to watch our movie now?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, darling", the matronly version says, smiling warmly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I think it's supposed to be a comedy", one of the other versions says, taking the seat next to you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "How many times have you seen this one?", the other asks.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "This will be my seventh", the one next to you says.
